h1. countHits

h2. Purpose

Executes a MongoDB [$text|http://docs.mongodb.org/manual/reference/operator/query/text/#op._S_text] search query and returns the number of hits.

h2. Examples

{code}
assert Product.countHits("coffee") == 5
{code}

h2. Description

The @countHits@ method uses MongoDB's full text search support to perform full text search on a "text" index and return the size of the returned cursor.